    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, with all major services performed according to the manufacturer's schedule. While the exterior and interior show some light, typical wear from regular use, there are no major mechanical issues or significant cosmetic damage. It offers a dependable driving experience for its next owner and is ready for the road.",
