      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD3S, featuring the iconic 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This example maintains its factory-spec longitudinal front-midship layout, delivering a perfect 50/50 weight distribution. Recent compression testing confirms healthy apex seals across all faces of both rotors. The chassis remains taut with original double-wishbone suspension components and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The cooling system has been meticulously maintained to prevent heat soak, ensuring the forced induction system operates at peak thermal efficiency. Finished in showroom-quality Montego Blue, this FD is an unmolested specimen of 90s JDM engineering, free of the common vacuum line degradation or subframe oxidation.",
